{"tid":797753,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"尋求英文寫作改善方法-認真討論","createTime":"2018-08-28T17:57:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-29T09:22:29.000Z","uid":119757,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"e09d22bb27e1b655192969e7ba8f61fe63fd00e4","tid":797753,"uid":119757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T17:57:51.000Z","msg":"小弟英文文筆不佳，常有組織以及文法問題。<br />\n想請教下各路英雄，有甚麼好路數。<br />\n除了由根基學起，還有甚麼方法去改進以上問題。<br />\n本人年事以高，難以從一般正常方法改善。<br />\n<br />\n如閣下並非認真討論<br />\n請按左上角離開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：教育程度已超越學士水平"},{"pid":"31f8e84acb9c130cb417b44592c7aec696168492","tid":797753,"uid":199016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T18:03:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cf3d68bb818f34f7e4abd5fd0654ad51a71c3d5d","tid":797753,"uid":44073,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T18:03:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9ba243e039a65eef126e4e29b1e10efddd406679","tid":797753,"uid":120814,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"e09d22bb27e1b655192969e7ba8f61fe63fd00e4","tid":797753,"uid":119757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T17:57:51.000Z","msg":"小弟英文文筆不佳，常有組織以及文法問題。<br />\n想請教下各路英雄，有甚麼好路數。<br />\n除了由根基學起，還有甚麼方法去改進以上問題。<br />\n本人年事以高，難以從一般正常方法改善。<br />\n<br />\n如閣下並非認真討論<br />\n請按左上角離開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：教育程度已超越學士水平"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T18:05:39.000Z","msg":"首先最緊要用字語境要正確, 例如寫formal野時唔好用太informal既野, <br />\n可簡即簡, 用最少字表達最多意思<br />\n善用標點, 用好表點符號好緊要, 可以慳返好多連接詞, <br />\n要再上一層樓就係對文化了解, 同幽默感<br />\n講到尾都係多寫多讀, 同睇你寫黎做咩, 咩文體"},{"pid":"f0237f6561bb843739f6ebd059ce8ab479cd22d2","tid":797753,"uid":126973,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T18:08:48.000Z","msg":"先練寫短句，愈簡單嘅句子愈好，唔好嫌弱智<br />\n保證文法正確<br />\n當你做到先再理文筆 用詞"},{"pid":"67b7e07bb9ad8b0bb8910208f38be65c494a46b1","tid":797753,"uid":171958,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f0237f6561bb843739f6ebd059ce8ab479cd22d2","tid":797753,"uid":126973,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T18:08:48.000Z","msg":"先練寫短句，愈簡單嘅句子愈好，唔好嫌弱智<br />\n保證文法正確<br />\n當你做到先再理文筆 用詞"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T18:12:50.000Z","msg":"同意，以前老師都係建議我寫短句保證文法岩先，之後再慢慢寫長句。<br />\n<br />\n利 英文一直麻麻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2db7434344592a8a69855c1fa0b0c38ed516535","tid":797753,"uid":192491,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T18:22:00.000Z","msg":"無論點, 都要練到寫得自然、idiomatic, <br />\n多啲記下usual words既collocations 同phrases<br />\n 唔好做壞手勢學深字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申: 英文垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2b043e28de140814a7ac47544ec6fa733e99caf","tid":797753,"uid":199016,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T18:23:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"933aa281a3de1aaf5e21bfc2a5fba69ef77c6f9d","tid":797753,"uid":199016,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T18:24:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b887424949b2669b4475271116515cc713b844b1","tid":797753,"uid":192491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"933aa281a3de1aaf5e21bfc2a5fba69ef77c6f9d","tid":797753,"uid":199016,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T18:24:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T19:05:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"735f1871cf242f6af78fea852b7107fac678fa29","tid":797753,"uid":199677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T03:09:23.000Z","msg":"始終都係覺得睇多啲書 或者甚至睇多啲片 等啲句型啊語境意思入下腦先真正用到岀嚟<br />\n<br />\n揾啲自己中意嘅書同片睇下就不知不覺進步到<br />\n<br />\n利申中學六年無乜點認真讀過學校教嘅syllabus"},{"pid":"958a18707cb009978da567f57666384c2f2f58f3","tid":797753,"uid":133896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T09:22:29.000Z","msg":"唔想寫嘢好chinglish或姐將一堆vocab亂咁塞黎用，可以有咩方法?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}